virtual ComFailure::Code Net::OutChannel::stub ( IOVectEntry *  iov,
size_t  count_iov 
) [pure virtual]

Client stub to write message An error with an error code is thrown in case of error. This error code is pass in parameter to the notification of the callback. If the method returns ASYNC_POST, it means that the data has been sent using non blocking method and the local completion should be test by calling test method.

Implemented in FDNET::OutChannel, MANET::OutChannel, MYNET::OutChannel, Net::BastOutChannel, SOCKNET::Channel, TAKTUKNET::OutChannel, UDPNET::OutChannel, FT::OutChannelIda, and FT::OChannelFile.

virtual ComFailure::Code Net::OutChannel::test (  )  [virtual]

Client to test end of completion of request on a channel An error with an error code is thrown in case of error. This error code is pass in parameter to the notification of the callback. If the method returns ASYNC_POST, then the pending operation is still pending.
